{"tid":799472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"申訴署：同一街市檔租相差90倍！　百三蚊VS萬二蚊","createTime":"2018-08-30T05:47:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T07:52:47.000Z","uid":150685,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cda6c8ca9487ab664a0e9b2dbcae34b158a51830","tid":799472,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:47:04.000Z","msg":"申訴專員公署主動調查公眾街市攤檔的租務管理，發現當中有多項不足，其中包括攤檔租金水平低及差距大，<span style=\"color: red;\">有位於同一街市的攤檔租金差距更相距達90倍，分別月租130港元及12,000港元</span>。<br />\n<br />\n申訴署指，食環署有24個公眾街市同時存有月租200港元以下及9000港元以上的攤檔，出現有2個在同一街市的攤擋，位置雖近在咫尺及面積相同，實際租金卻相差超過70至90倍情況；另有76%的街市攤檔租金低於市場水平。申訴署認為，此舉造成街市不公平競爭。<br />\n<br />\n申訴署又指現時食環署不限制檔主租用檔口的數目，變相助長濫用攤檔及減少市民的購物選擇，有街市的兩名檔主分別租用23個及11個攤檔，全用作賣花，有街市更有1檔主租用23個攤檔，全用作儲存貨物。<br />\n<br />\n申訴專員劉燕卿指，由於公眾街市不少攤檔的租金水平低，令食環署長期以公帑補貼街市，過去5年，食環署營運公眾街市的赤字高達16億港元。即使攤檔租金低，但所售賣的貨品價格與其他街市或攤檔沒太大差別，反映租金便宜但未有惠及市民。<br />\n<br />\n申訴署促請食環署檢討以低於市場租金為底價的競投模式，全面檢討租金調整機制，及就租出攤檔的數量設上限等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180830/bkn-20180830104802913-0830_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180830%2Fbkn-20180830104802913-0830_00822_001.html&d=EYS8dUhnf9IpOxqvfzW2Q0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=3f10f342\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180830/bkn-20180830104802913-0830_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c511651a0e9ab6b2bcaf0486e1a08cba15c23d95","tid":799472,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"將來食環署街市物價，或會與商營街市物價接軌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb033fdaf4ab72ae9d2b7fe007bb6f5e8fa2b4db","tid":799472,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"賣畀領匯咪得。"},{"pid":"f879252c1d0ff7fa78bc2144d50b792aba141614","tid":799472,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb033fdaf4ab72ae9d2b7fe007bb6f5e8fa2b4db","tid":799472,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"賣畀領匯咪得。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"大家齊齊90000租 夠公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"896ba70a81327e4a2b6fcfc792aa04ca929263bb","tid":799472,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f879252c1d0ff7fa78bc2144d50b792aba141614","tid":799472,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb033fdaf4ab72ae9d2b7fe007bb6f5e8fa2b4db","tid":799472,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T05:55:23.000Z","msg":"賣畀領匯咪得。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:14:31.000Z","msg":"大家齊齊90000租 夠公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:15:36.000Z","msg":"然後再分拆賣俾人<br />\n<br />\n90000 變900000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19facfa4f7c95aa65fd345ffc9be9e3cf93c31d7","tid":799472,"uid":99584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:18:23.000Z","msg":"平租唔平賣, 要賺盡, 最後咪攬炒囉"},{"pid":"0c112b21ceaf8336b12690271cb42fbc992f3f50","tid":799472,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T07:49:00.000Z","msg":"連做小生意都有錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da18a93b615e2a031549d661192e8b7c4b21b71","tid":799472,"uid":121333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T07:52:18.000Z","msg":"唔講真係唔知，可以百幾蚊租咁低，租金平過食放題，咁咪賺到家肥屋潤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac87421e8c0fc7d7be66f37f6f0b6332f055f3b","tid":799472,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19facfa4f7c95aa65fd345ffc9be9e3cf93c31d7","tid":799472,"uid":99584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T06:18:23.000Z","msg":"平租唔平賣, 要賺盡, 最後咪攬炒囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-30T07:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm